class aos.client.AosClient(protocol: str, host: str, port: int, session: requests.sessions.Session = None)[source]¶

Bases: object

Establish, maintain and interact with an AOS server session

Parameters

  • protocol – (str) https or http connection to AOS api

  • host – (str) AOS server url or ip address

  • port – (int) AOS server port (ex 80, 443)

  • session – (obj) Established session with AOS server
